Class WebappMinifierMojo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.maven.plugin.AbstractMojo
      • com.github.webapp_minifier.WebappMinifierMojo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OverridablePluginOptions, PluginOptions, org.apache.maven.plugin.ContextEnabled, org.apache.maven.plugin.Mojo

    @Mojo(name="minify-webapp",
      defaultPhase=PREPARE_PACKAGE,
      threadSafe=true,
      requiresDependencyResolution=COMPILE)
public class WebappMinifierMojo
extends org.apache.maven.plugin.AbstractMojo
implements PluginOptions
    Minifies the web application.
